# Sensitive security working notes — keep LOCAL only, never commit to the
# public repo. priority-fixes.md is the live audit queue (attack paths +
# unverified fixes); docs/security/private/ is for any future sensitive notes.
# Public, non-sensitive security docs (e.g. api-docs-policy.md) stay tracked.
docs/security/priority-fixes.md
docs/security/private/
